@baseUrl = http://localhost:5000/api/v1
@contentType = application/json

# ==============================================================================
# COMMISSION
# ==============================================================================

### GET commission summary (custom date range)
GET {{baseUrl}}/commission/summary?startDate=1773000000000&endDate=1773999999999
Content-Type: {{contentType}}

###

### GET commission summary (today)
GET {{baseUrl}}/commission/summary?startDate=1773744000000&endDate=1773830399999
Content-Type: {{contentType}}

###

### GET commission summary (missing startDate — expect 400)
GET {{baseUrl}}/commission/summary?endDate=1773999999999
Content-Type: {{contentType}}

###

### GET commission summary (missing endDate — expect 400)
GET {{baseUrl}}/commission/summary?startDate=1773000000000
Content-Type: {{contentType}}

###

### GET commission summary (startDate > endDate — expect 400)
GET {{baseUrl}}/commission/summary?startDate=1773999999999&endDate=1773000000000
Content-Type: {{contentType}}